Competition: Copa America
Season: 1919
Country: Brazil
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tables/19safull.html

* Brazil, 11-29 May. All games played in Río de Janeiro. Originally dated to 1918, but a flu epidemy delayed it.

11.05.19  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
BRA - CHI 6:0 (3:0)
(20,000) Juan Pedro Barbera ARG
BRA: Marcos - Píndaro, Bianco - Sergio I, Amílcar, Galo - Luiz Meneses, Neco, Friedenreich,Haroldo, Arnaldo
CHI: Guerrero - Gatica, Poirier - Baeza, González, Domínguez - Báez, Fuentes, France, Muñoz,Varas
1:0 Friedenreich 19, 2:0 Neco 21, 3:0 Friedenreich 38, 4:0 Friedenreich 76, 5:0 Haroldo 79,6:0 Neco 83

13.05.19  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
URU -ARG 3:2 (2:1)
(18,000) Robert L. Todd ENG
URU: Saporiti - Varela, Foglino - Delgado, Zibechi, Vanzzino - Pérez, H.Scarone, C.Scarone,Gradín, Romano
ARG: Isola - Cortella, Reyes - Mattozzi, Uslenghi, Martínez - Calomino, Laiolo, Clarcke,Izaguirre, Perinetti
1:0 C.Scarone 19, 2:0 H.Scarone 23, 2:1 Izaguirre 34, 2:2 Varela 79 o, 3:2 Gradín 85

